    <h1 class="text-headline-lg font-display text-inverse-on-surface mb-4 max-w-2xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-body-lg text-inverse-on-surface/70 max-w-xl">
      This privacy policy applies to all products and services offered by AKA Digital or its subsidiaries or affiliated companies.
    </p>
    <p class="text-label-md text-inverse-on-surface/40 mt-6">Last updated: 2016 · AKA Digital Pte. Ltd.</p>
